e; de votre site.</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"SEOMix : WordCamp Europe et le bonheur de l’Open Source";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:37:"http://www.seomix.fr/wordcamp-europe/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:37:"http://www.seomix.fr/wordcamp-europe/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2013-10-15T08:30:42+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"anonymous";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1462:"<div>\n<div><img width="180" height="52" src="http://www.seomix.fr/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/wordcamp-europe-salle-180x52.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Salle comble au Wordcamp Europe"></div>Le WordCamp Europe 2013 est termin&eacute;, et est pourtant l''un des meilleurs &eacute;v&egrave;nements sur WP &agrave; ne pas manquer. Le coeur de ces 3 jours: la force de l''Open Source !\n      <p><strong>Article original :</strong> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.seomix.fr/wordcamp-europe/">WordCamp Europe et le bonheur de l&rsquo;Open Source</a>.</p>\n      <p><strong>Debut du contenu :</strong> Le weekend dernier avait lieu le tout premier WordCamp Europe. Pour ceux qui ne savent pas ce qu''est un WordCamp, c''est un rassemblement de geeks et professionnels tous aussi fans les uns des autres de ce CMS. L''&eacute;tat d''esprit : le partage et l''&eacute;change. 3 jours de pur plaisir Ce qui est g&eacute;nial, c''est la passion et l''engouement que peuvent avoir l''ensemble des participants et conf&eacute;renciers. Le Road Trip incluait une sacr&eacute; DreamTeam de Fran&ccedil;ais pr&ecirc;ts &agrave; en d&eacute;coudre avec WP. Contrairement aux autres &eacute;v&egrave;nements auxquels j''ai d&eacute;j&agrave; particip&eacute; sur le e-marketing ou le SEO, l''&eacute;tat d''esprit est plus ouvert [&hellip;]</p>\n<hr>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/seomix-wordpress/~4/DGTD_iU7JZw" height="1" width="1">\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:90:"WordPress Francophone : L’Hebdo WordPress n° 203 : WordCamp Europe – Jetpack – 2014";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:67:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/I_T29yH-XB4/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:67:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/I_T29yH-XB4/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2013-10-15T07:50:21+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"anonymous";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4133:"<div>\n<h3>WordCamp Europe 2013</h3>\n<p>Les retours sur le premier WordCamp Europe continuent :</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.595283903862447&amp;type=3&amp;l=4b5ed6fdcf">Les photos de Ptah Dunbar</a></li>\n<li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://veryfrenchtrip-wp.eu/ce-que-jai-appris-a-wordcamp-europe">Ce que Jenny Beaumont a appris</a></li>\n<li>\n<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://speakerdeck.com/tammielis/the-life-of-a-theme">La vie d&rsquo;un th&egrave;me (en)</a> selon Tammie Lister (conf&eacute;rence)</li>\n<li>\n<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://imhugo.com/blog/events/wordcamp-europe-2013-building-the-future/">Construire le futur (en)</a> par Hugo</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Ap&eacute;ro WordPress &agrave; Lyon</h3>\n<p>Pour ceux qui n&rsquo;ont pas pu se rendre &agrave; Leyden pour le WordCamp Europe (et qui habitent la r&eacute;gion lyonnaise), <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://aperowordpress.eventbrite.fr/">un ap&eacute;ro est organis&eacute; par Jonathan ce vendredi</a>.</p>\n<h3>Jetpack : Infinite scroll et th&egrave;me enfant</h3>\n<p>D&eacute;couvrez comment configurer Jetpack dans le cadre d&rsquo;<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://jetpack.me/2013/10/10/how-to-override-jetpack-infinite-scroll-settings-in-a-child-theme/">un th&egrave;me enfant avec la fonction infinite scroll (en)</a>.</p>\n<h3>2014 : des nouvelles du front</h3>\n<p>Le <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://make.wordpress.org/core/2013/10/11/twenty-fourteen-project-update-2/">d&eacute;veloppement du futur th&egrave;me par d&eacute;faut (en)</a>&nbsp;avance.</p>\n<h3>Sondage 2013</h3>\n<p>Comme r&eacute;guli&egrave;rement, chaque ann&eacute;e, un sondage est cr&eacute;&eacute; afin de connaitre les avis de la communaut&eacute; sur les prochains d&eacute;veloppements de WordPress. <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wp-survey.polldaddy.com/s/wp-2013?src=pio">A vous la parole (en)</a>.</p>\n<h3>Personnaliser l&rsquo;&eacute;cran de connexion</h3>\n<p>L&rsquo;&eacute;cran de connexion de WordPress est toujours le m&ecirc;me, <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wp.tutsplus.com/tutorials/creative-coding/customizing-the-wordpress-admin-the-login-screen/">pourquoi ne pas le personnalise (en)</a>&nbsp;?</p>\n<h3>Un framework gratuit</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://marketpress.com/feedback/xtreme-one-1-6-open-beta-free-download/">Xtreme One est un th&egrave;me framework</a>, il est propos&eacute; gratuitement.</p>\n<h3>WP de France</h3>\n<p>Une nouvelle vitrine de sites WordPress vient compl&eacute;ter l&rsquo;offre de la <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.wordpress-fr.net/vitrine/">vitrine propos&eacute;e par WordPress Francophone</a> en proposant d&rsquo;autres sites remarquables propuls&eacute;s par WordPress&hellip; et toujours en fran&ccedil;ais. Bienvenue &agrave; <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wpdefrance.fr/">WP de France</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=I_T29yH-XB4:2JxdyHkdV0Q:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=I_T29yH-XB4:2JxdyHkdV0Q:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=I_T29yH-XB4:2JxdyHkdV0Q:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=I_T29yH-XB4:2JxdyHkdV0Q:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=I_T29yH-XB4:2JxdyHkdV0Q:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=I_T29yH-XB4:2JxdyHkdV0Q:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></a>\n</div>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/I_T29yH-XB4" height="1" width="1">\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:61:"L''écho des plugins WordPress : Menu Items Visibility Control";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:75:"http://www.echodesplugins.li-an.fr/plugins/menu-items-visibility-control-2/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:75:"http://www.echodesplugins.li-an.fr/plugins/menu-items-visibility-control-2/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_